# Booking Card

## Summary
The `Booking` card represents a booking or event that has a venue, start and end times, hosts, and optional sponsors.

## Import
```javascript
import { Booking } from './booking';
```

## Usage as a Field
You can use the `Booking` card as a field within a consuming card or field:

```javascript
import { contains, CardDef, field } from 'https://cardstack.com/base/card-api';
import { Booking } from './booking';

export class Event extends CardDef {
  @field booking = contains(Booking);
}
```

## Template Usage
Inside the template of a consuming card or field, you can display the `Booking` information like this:

```hbs
<h2><@fields.booking.cardTitle /></h2>
<div><@fields.booking.startTime /> to <@fields.booking.endTime /></div>
<div>Hosted by: <@fields.booking.hosts /></div>
```
